Package: mpi
Type: Package
Title: Multidimensional Poverty Index (Alkire-Foster Method)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Julien Bidias [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Julien Bidias <julienbidias246@gmail.com>
Description: This package computes the Multidimensional Poverty Index (MPI) 
    using the Alkire-Foster methodology. It allows users to supply binary 
    deprivation indicators, assign weights, and specify a poverty cutoff. 
    The function returns key statistics (H, A, MPI) and generates an 
    interactive Plotly bar chart of poverty status.
